      "title": "Ranil Wickramasinghe takes oath as Acting President before the Chief Justice",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A spokesman for the Prime Minister's Office told BBC Sinhala that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe was sworn in as Acting President today (July 15) in front of Chief Justice Jayantha Jayasuriya.",
        "He said that Ranil Wickramasinghe was sworn in as Acting President in Colombo."
